Anthony Sagar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Sagar 0 Anthony Sagar (19 June 1920 – 24 January 1973) was an English character actor and a member of the National Theatre. Although rarely receiving top billing, he was regarded as a stalwart and appeared in many well-known films (including seven of the Carry On series) and in many television sitcoms and dramas such as The Moonstone, Dad's Army, The Avengers and Steptoe and Son.
